2) Write a program to benchmark the performance of reduce, all-reduce,
broadcast as a function of both N and P.  Use N=1,2,4,8,...,1024*1024
doubles. And experiment with processes on the same node and on
different nodes (this means setting #nodes and #ppn correctly in the
PBS file).  How to verify you have set these correctly?

3) Parallelize the recursively adaptive quadrature program global/recursive.cc.

